replies.message: We understand your concerns, Chelon. If you want the video to be removed from Facebook, you can send a message to your friend asking them to take it down. You can also block the person who tagged you, which removes the tag and prevents them from tagging you in any other videos. Learn more: http://bit.ly/2ixq03M. -Hannah
